group.name: Weekly French Lessons Brussels - Quick & efficient learning

description:
1)  Focusing on the 4/5 complicated sound of the French language

Gives a good base for beginners and checks the correct pronunciation for the advanced.

2) Quickly introduce yourself – Question and answer (Name/age/Nationality/Job/Hobbies)

3) How to formulate a question (Cost/Travels/Reasons/Goal/ Directions…)

4) DAILY LIFE: French expressions! (Daily conversational words)

5) Describing someone physically and morally (adjectives)

6) Different persons (I,You,She/he…)

7) Post-it game to summarize 

-Different hours in the week corresponding to working hours (Monday and Tuesday at 6.30 P.M, Friday at 5 P.M)
-I can teach french for specific needs (interview for a job etc..)
-Group of 6 maximum for conversation and game
-Focus on oral and get rid of tricky part of the french language
-Interesting price: 10 euros per class!

description:
You want to learn french and try the different programs offered in Brussels? This session is the occasion to discover the Learn French Quickly Program. Adapted to begginers, it would be a good first step into the french language.

The price is reduced to 2 € for one hour

The program of the session is:
- 2 easiest french tenses: past and future
-Vocabulary of meetings
-Time indicator
Optional (according to time): numbers and hours
